165
00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:20.476
No. you cannot kick
me out. I am his mother.

166
00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:22.116
- With all due respect. i-i...
- No. no. I'm gonna report your ass

167
00:08:22.140 --> 00:08:23.276
- to Cal fire so fast.
- You need... I-I need

168
00:08:23.300 --> 00:08:25.846
