178
00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:49.200
But you made it. Don't give up now.

179
00:08:50.060 --> 00:08:51.700
Stay close.

180
00:08:56.740 --> 00:08:59.416
I.c.. I've got eyes on a downed engine.

181
